Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.29,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,所以才说你心不在焉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.36,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你是二年一班的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:17.53,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.70,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,认识相麻同学么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:21.84,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.45,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,那就好 我是被她叫来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.79,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,知道她人在哪么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:28.02,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.13,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:33.59,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.30,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,讨厌吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:36.71,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.16,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,觉得我和你像么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.71,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,要看「像」的概念该如何定义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.92,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,那 你在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.61,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,如果想一个人躲著的话我就离开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.85,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,我是被相麻堇叫到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.15,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,并非想一个人躲著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:59.38,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,这些话 如果在刚才问到相麻同学时能听到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.70,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,你和相麻同学经常交谈么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:07.02,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,一年级时的所有同学中与我互通言语最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.25,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,就是相麻堇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.02,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,那你们关系不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:14.44,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,升入二年级后 在学校与我互通言语最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:15.59,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.40,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,「Reset.」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.98,sagrad reset,,0,0,0,,那个人…
