Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:40.61,RESET OP CH - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}令未来循声而至
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:51.50,RESET OP CH - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}我驻足叩问内心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:59.28,RESET OP CH - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}世界将如何展现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:11.05,RESET OP CH - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}在理想与现实的罅隙之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:21.48,RESET OP CH - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}时钟的指针便从此处踏步
